Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,===========PART1===========
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.18,0:01:36.83,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真刺激！可怕的头上冷气
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.21,0:03:01.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么在这样的热天还…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.07,0:03:04.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我见到心烦的脸
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.31,0:03:07.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,任何方面都心烦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.35,0:04:13.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂！阿当
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.63,0:04:16.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,石门水库开了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.02,0:04:21.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这种放荡的行为
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.59,0:04:23.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才会招致今日日本的腐败
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.35,0:04:25.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而导致世界末日
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.00,0:04:26.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啰嗦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.97,0:04:29.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你难道不懂这是为让多一点的风送入
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.07,0:04:31.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我所想的方法吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.00,0:04:33.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们给我住口
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.65,0:04:36.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,低级的争执 听得耳朵都会腐烂
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.40,0:04:58.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂！再转一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.56,0:05:19.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂！在干什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.30,0:05:56.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.04,0:06:25.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.07,0:06:27.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.29,0:06:41.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们干什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.17,0:06:53.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.62,0:07:11.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.27,0:07:13.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,May I ask you (a) special favor?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.41,0:07:16.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.00,0:07:19.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Would you please take my picture
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.05,0:07:20.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,with this camera?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.41,0:07:22.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.57,0:07:24.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'd be glad to.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.02,0:07:26.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.54,0:07:51.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.80,0:07:55.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天气这么热 别乱闹了好么？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.32,0:07:57.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对！对！这会越来越热的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.00,0:08:02.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家为什么都那么沉不住气
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.71,0:08:04.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别问些当然的事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.82,0:08:06.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反而愈加的火大
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.68,0:08:09.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还真能保持那凉快的脸
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.22,0:08:10.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很凉快啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.15,0:08:14.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.51,0:08:17.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是冰冷气
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.81,0:08:24.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你居然独享这种东西
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.33,0:08:28.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是地球人的精神力实在无法支撑
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.97,0:08:30.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,念力么？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.84,0:08:32.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是平常心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.84,0:08:34.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平常心？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.32,0:08:35.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.13,0:08:38.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是放轻松就能够支撑
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.43,0:08:40.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么 简单嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.27,0:08:41.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这还有吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.77,0:08:44.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请分一点 拉姆小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.36,0:08:45.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉姆 拿出来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.96,0:08:47.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样下去无法上课了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.62,0:08:49.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的可以吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.01,0:08:51.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还藏什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.70,0:08:53.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快拿出来啊！快！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.86,0:09:02.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放轻松哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.27,0:09:16.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是那个班
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.01,0:09:19.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样总算能上课了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.34,0:09:21.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 大家到座位上
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.67,0:09:25.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真凉爽
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.08,0:09:30.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坐到座位上！你们听不懂么！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.34,0:09:36.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.16,0:09:37.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.52,0:09:40.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果平常心有所扰动就会遭天谴
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.98,0:09:43.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真让人有点紧张的冷气
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.86,0:09:45.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.25,0:09:47.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轻松…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.12,0:09:49.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.49,0:09:58.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你突然间做什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.67,0:10:02.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…别恶作剧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.94,0:10:04.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.75,0:10:07.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么开始上课吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.54,0:10:11.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦！老是这么快就恢复了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.12,0:10:13.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么点小事不会倒下的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.42,0:10:14.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上课吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.59,0:10:15.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.74,0:10:20.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 越来越有人情味了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.71,0:10:30.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果那样勉强笑积存怨气的话就
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.45,0:10:35.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遇到万一之时就不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.13,0:10:36.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.94,0:10:39.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这危险物品我不要
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.06,0:10:41.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正也凉快了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.78,0:10:44.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就请回收吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.05,0:10:46.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不到冬天不会融化！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.65,0:10:50.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这话是开玩笑的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.36,0:10:52.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.93,0:10:54.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像能适应了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.86,0:10:56.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底会持续多久呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.83,0:10:58.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个小时
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.01,0:11:00.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个小时
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.33,0:11:01.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像感觉很短
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.80,0:11:05.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但要保持平常心就太长了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.67,0:11:10.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就要看平时的精神意志了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.92,0:11:18.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要嘛 不要急积存怨气嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.80,0:11:19.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也对！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.73,0:11:21.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不论怎么说
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.46,0:11:25.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先想法子融化才是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.27,0:11:27.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是愚蠢的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.31,0:11:29.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心头灭却 色即是空
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.08,0:11:41.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别积嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.97,0:11:50.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是太阳最快
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.69,0:11:54.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么热的天别挤啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.84,0:11:57.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法嘛 窗户小嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.70,0:11:59.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别挤！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.76,0:12:01.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别挤啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.33,0:12:02.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你才是！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.49,0:12:04.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很热啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.49,0:12:18.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.15,0:00:01.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,===========PART2===========
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.18,0:12:42.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位平常心 保持轻松
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.61,0:13:00.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们上课中在做些什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.90,0:13:02.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轻松啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.72,0:13:05.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事呢 校长？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.90,0:13:07.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在生气啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.63,0:13:10.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而你们有什么好乐的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.72,0:13:13.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,校长 这是有原因的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.60,0:13:16.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好的站着！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.06,0:13:17.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.06,0:13:21.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.52,0:13:27.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这算什么态度
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.62,0:13:28.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以校长啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.87,0:13:32.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在不能展现紧迫感啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.13,0:13:32.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.78,0:13:33.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我了解了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.86,0:13:36.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们把我当傻子是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.58,0:13:38.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.04,0:13:40.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们正和自己作战
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.58,0:13:41.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.31,0:13:42.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,立正
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.29,0:13:45.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,俯卧撑一百次 仰卧起坐二百次
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.56,0:13:48.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样下去不是办法
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.42,0:13:51.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃课…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.77,0:13:54.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轻松…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.97,0:13:54.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃课…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.81,0:13:57.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轻松…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.31,0:13:57.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃课…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.19,0:14:01.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃课…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.42,0:14:04.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃课…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.20,0:14:04.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.01,0:14:07.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃课…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.11,0:14:10.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃课…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.01,0:14:14.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不能一直这么做
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.41,0:14:15.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.83,0:14:18.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 好像呆子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.33,0:14:19.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃课
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.31,0:14:22.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羞耻
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.05,0:14:24.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天之怜悯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.04,0:14:29.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用红外线融化吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.36,0:14:31.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好热
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.62,0:14:33.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好冷
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.78,0:14:36.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好热
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.25,0:14:38.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不冷 不热
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.64,0:14:45.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样只会积存憋闷之气
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.07,0:14:56.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反而变大了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.94,0:14:58.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们在做什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.69,0:15:01.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在头上浮什么冰嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.17,0:15:02.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来得正是时候
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.56,0:15:04.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鬼天 喷火！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.91,0:15:07.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.31,0:15:11.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁说向我喷的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.30,0:15:12.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉姆姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.91,0:15:14.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是冰冷气吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.60,0:15:15.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.29,0:15:17.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.91,0:15:23.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.47,0:15:29.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.32,0:15:58.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真无法相信
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.19,0:15:59.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是不合常理的可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.62,0:16:01.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉姆小姐 这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.51,0:16:03.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我从来就不知道…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.51,0:16:06.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,写些什么呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.14,0:16:08.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怨气超过一定量之后
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.38,0:16:12.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在冰冷气中会出现本人的妄想
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.18,0:16:13.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会这样！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.49,0:16:14.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,达令
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.88,0:16:17.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么色的妄想 我可会生气的！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.79,0:16:18.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,色？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.54,0:16:19.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说什么话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.62,0:16:21.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是艺术
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.08,0:16:24.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦！美 史上之美！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.63,0:16:27.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,达令
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.75,0:16:30.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的触摸法太色了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.01,0:16:50.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 诸星
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.96,0:16:52.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要去哪！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.14,0:16:56.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男人有无理由想独处的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.58,0:16:58.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别睁眼说瞎话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.41,0:17:00.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一定想一个人把冰融化
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.27,0:17:01.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与取出的樱花小姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.43,0:17:02.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼镜
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.45,0:17:05.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你头上也有冰冷气哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.11,0:17:06.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.11,0:17:11.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想从那里得到拉姆是办得到的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.40,0:17:14.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妄想不会是妄想的现实
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.57,0:17:15.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在你头上
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.76,0:17:17.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧 面堂
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.82,0:17:20.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.83,0:17:21.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会让你走的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.90,0:17:24.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,樱花小姐由我们保护
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.04,0:17:25.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.09,0:17:26.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能因为你偷腥的毛病
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.52,0:17:28.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使拉姆小姐哭泣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.37,0:17:33.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小天 快把冰融掉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.63,0:17:36.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手 小鬼天
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.67,0:17:41.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放手 快放手
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.96,0:17:44.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不放！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.89,0:18:15.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.59,0:18:16.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.11,0:18:18.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真无法相信
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.11,0:18:20.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冰中有我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.56,0:18:21.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.27,0:18:24.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.38,0:18:25.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有冰装的我！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.07,0:18:27.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.33,0:18:33.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽管是妄想的产物
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.26,0:18:34.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.61,0:18:35.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.23,0:18:39.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,决不能落入阿当手中
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.29,0:18:41.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.13,0:18:43.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝不能让诸星跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.67,0:18:46.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要以我们的手 保护柔弱的她们
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.69,0:18:50.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对！怎能让诸星自己好过
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.44,0:18:54.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真没用的伪善者
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.28,0:18:56.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好看着
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.22,0:19:00.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,达令 做什么 疯了…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.61,0:19:03.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这小子 自己积自己的怨气
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.09,0:19:20.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.68,0:19:24.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要以她们建立究极的后宫
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.48,0:19:26.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,究极的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.43,0:19:27.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后宫
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.09,0:19:44.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,达令！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.75,0:19:47.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉姆小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.81,0:19:51.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼镜捉住诸星
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.97,0:20:11.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总算了解了吧 面堂
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.30,0:20:13.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也不用忍了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.07,0:20:18.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真没用的一群
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.74,0:20:20.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知不知道羞耻
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.88,0:20:57.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么这样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.27,0:20:59.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看不下去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.74,0:21:16.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家把头抬起来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.05,0:21:20.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然依靠妄想！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.91,0:21:25.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让你了解活生生女孩的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.95,0:21:41.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愚蠢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.00,0:21:45.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就如想象的被自己设的陷阱陷害
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.49,0:21:48.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冰里的我们会变成怎样
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.66,0:21:50.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有等它融了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.43,0:22:07.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,达令
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.12,0:22:18.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,醒了啊 拉姆
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.45,0:22:19.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.59,0:22:22.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冰里的不融？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.60,0:22:24.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不必担心
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.21,0:22:25.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仔细看看
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.24,0:22:45.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随着冰的融解
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.89,0:22:47.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妄想也居然一起融了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.71,0:22:49.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,害我自己担心了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.65,0:22:51.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是烦人的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.84,0:22:58.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然地球人还是不行
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.09,0:23:07.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是无可救药的学生
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.09,0:23:14.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要这样看我
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.19,0:23:20.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然身为教育家
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.91,0:23:24.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也有满溢的思绪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.15,0:00:01.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,===========预告===========
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.35,0:23:53.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为纪念孟夏在亚空间买花
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.88,0:23:56.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为这样 这个月零用钱没了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.69,0:23:59.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是锁定目标 注入思绪
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.38,0:24:00.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,射！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.50,0:24:01.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.21,0:24:04.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱的袭击！无法停止的罗曼蒂克！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.47,0:24:05.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.15,0:00:01.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,===========OP===========
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.35,0:00:20.88,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手法虽早已被看穿 而正是这点却十分可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.88,0:00:29.63,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你用五分的傲气对我 我接受你的挑战 好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.63,0:00:37.46,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高高地 将脚翘起 送秋波 就差一点点
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.53,0:00:41.13,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多么的绚烂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.33,0:00:52.23,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鼓动起来的微热  湿润的眼瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.23,0:00:55.53,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 你正看着我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.53,0:01:02.03,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也看着你  是不是太有魅力了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.03,0:01:09.13,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我们尽情欢乐  今夜的你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.13,0:01:12.93,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将无法入睡 woo
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.15,0:00:01.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,===========ED===========
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.75,0:24:20.25,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是多么的美好  不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.25,0:24:24.45,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在的话还来得及
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.45,0:24:26.65,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是多么的美好
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.65,0:24:34.05,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在天空有鸟飞翔之时
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.55,0:24:48.35,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地球真是个美丽的星球 漂浮在宇宙里
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.35,0:24:55.30,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,独一无二的绿洲
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.30,0:25:01.35,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祝你好运   替你守护着
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.35,0:25:10.00,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你所居住的那爱之星球
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.00,0:25:12.25,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是多么的刺激
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.25,0:25:17.05,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祝你好运   从这里发出的
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.05,0:25:25.05,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永远含有爱的心电感应
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.65,0:25:31.25,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是多么的刺激
